  {
    "id": "1714b3a6-9f61-4b80-aa04-6fed40ed036e",
    "sentence": "If that test is met, a reduction in our policy rate could be on the table as soon as the next meeting in September. So you asked, why not today? And I would just say, again, that the broad sense of the Committee is that we're getting closer to the point at which it will be appropriate to reduce our policy rate but that we're not quite at that point yet.",
