    "sen": "",
    "ten": "",
    "hor": "",
    "com": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "df5c3e43-78a7-493a-a761-c6abea6e9ad8",
    "sentence": "In the meantime, as that time approaches, we will be devoting a lot of careful thought and planning to the contours of it.",
