    "doc_type": "press_conference_qa",
    "date": "20240612",
    "context_question": "Thank you, Chair Powell. Evan Ryser with Market News International. You have mentioned before the framework review process will start in the latter half of the year. At this point, do you have any specific time frame for the start of that? Who will lead it? Will you be—will it be you or a member—a Committee group of your—of your peers? What will be the parameters? Do you anticipate the review will consider changes in communications going forward?",
