    "doc_type": "press_conference_qa",
    "date": "20121212",
    "context_question": "Last but not least, Greg Robb, MarketWatch. There seems to be growing evidence that some of the MBS purchases, the impact of the MBS purchases, are that banks are holding on to some of the gains and not passing them on to the borrowers. Is there anything you can do about that and are you concerned about that? Thank you.",
