    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "dfdc80e4-a9dd-4f2d-a04f-dae48346dd64",
    "sentence": "But, honestly, we don't know what that's going to be.",
    "source": "FOMCpresconf20220615.json",
    "doc_type": "press_conference_qa",
    "date": "20220615",
    "context_question": "Just given the illiquidity and extraordinary volatility in financial markets, whether QT will make things worse.",
