  {
    "id": "21f01ca6-33e4-4f61-82cd-9ffdc516efc1",
    "sentence": "So, you know, I, I was here -- we had all the same questions back in -- after the Global Financial Crisis.",
    "source": "FOMCpresconf20210127.json",
    "doc_type": "press_conference_qa",
    "date": "20210127",
    "context_question": "Well, if I might, you—your policies are working, and you can maybe do more. But the question is, can you stop doing it when it’s time?",
